### 1. Tambah Produk baru (Electronic)
POST http://localhost:8082/product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Smartphone XYZ",
  "description": "Smartphone dengan kamera AI dan baterai tahan lama.",
  "category": "Electronic",
  "price": 4999999,
  "stock": 120,
  "tags": ["electronic", "smartphone", "best-seller"]
}

### 2. Ambil Semua Produk
GET http://localhost:8082/products

### 3. Update Harga Produk berdasarkan ID
# Ganti {id} dengan ID produk yang dihasilkan oleh request create.
PUT http://localhost:8082/product/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Smartphone XYZ",
  "description": "Smartphone dengan kamera AI dan baterai tahan lama.",
  "category": "Electronic",
  "price": 4599999,
  "stock": 120,
  "tags": ["electronic", "smartphone", "promo"]
}

### 4. Cari Produk dengan kategori "Fashion" dan rentang harga tertentu
GET http://localhost:8082/products?category=Fashion&min_price=200000&max_price=2000000

### 5. Hapus Produk
# Ganti {id} dengan ID produk yang ingin dihapus.
DELETE http://localhost:8082/product/{id}
